w:r.w:t: This rating reflects your use of MI skills to highlight and strengthen the patient’s own reasons for making a change.
This rating reflects your use of MI skills to validate the patient’s barriers to change and guide them to consider possible reasons for change.
This rating reflects your use of skills designed to build a collaborative working relationship with your patient, consistent with the Spirit of MI.
This rating reflects your use of skills designed to express warmth and understanding of your patient within their unique circumstances, consistent with the Spirit of MI.
